                        <h1>Uzman görü&#351;leri - PetroChina</h1>
                        <p xmlns="">
                            <strong>Mobil Delvac 1</strong>&trade;<strong> 5W-40 ve Mühendislik servisi, y&#305;lda 12.000 US$&rsquo;&#305;n üzerinde tasarruf sa&#287;l&#305;yor</strong>
                        </p>
                        <p xmlns="">
                            <strong><img src="../Shared-Images-LCW/article_150x150_petro-china_gbl.jpg" height="150" width="150" alt="PetroChina" title="PetroChina" align="left" border="0" hspace="0" class="imgFloatLeft"></strong><strong><strong>Chinese North-Benz 2629 Kamyon Motorlar&#305;<br>
